        <p>
            In the evening Seb and I made ourselves comfortable at a café right by the harbor. Our accommodation had a side sea view and could also be seen. Two bathrooms, a large kitchen-living room and a nice large room for each couple.
        </p>
        <p>
            We would have loved to stay here much longer. But as often happens, you end up at the most beautiful accommodations only at the very end of the trip.
